524
01:02:35,602 --> 01:02:37,669
Don't fight it.

525
01:02:40,507 --> 01:02:42,442
That's it.

526
01:02:42,842 --> 01:02:44,909
That's good.

527
01:02:53,187 --> 01:02:57,157
You are awake... in your dream.

528
01:02:57,861 --> 01:02:59,359
That's good.

529
