(WIND HOWLING)

531
01:03:05,766 --> 01:03:07,467
...paralyzed.

532
01:03:07,567 --> 01:03:09,443
(WIND HOWLING)

533
01:03:10,898 --> 01:03:12,806
That's good.

534
01:03:12,906 --> 01:03:13,974
That's good.

535
01:03:14,074 --> 01:03:15,941
(WIND HOWLING)

536
01:03:50,210 --> 01:03:52,100
