PAUL: Have a good rest?

547
01:06:12,052 --> 01:06:14,087
'Cause I didn't.

548
01:06:14,387 --> 01:06:16,256
Spent the night worried about you.

549
01:06:16,356 --> 01:06:18,468
Feeling guilty about
swapping out your drugs.

550
01:06:21,595 --> 01:06:23,261
But then I discovered this.

551
