- (KEYBOARD CLICKING)
- Wednesday. Thursday.

552
01:06:32,541 --> 01:06:34,380
Friday.

553
01:06:34,741 --> 01:06:36,674
Sunday.

554
01:06:40,680 --> 01:06:42,113
Where's Saturday, Anna?

555
01:06:44,951 --> 01:06:47,220
I... I don't know.

556
01:06:47,320 --> 01:06:49,790
That's weird because...

557
01:06:49,890 --> 01:06:52,791
Saturday's the night
you were here by yourself.

558
01:06:56,530 --> 01:06:58,563
Let me show you something.

559
01:07:08,408 --> 01:07:11,742
I couldn't really care less
about the surveillance cameras.

560
01:07:12,412 --> 01:07:15,746
Well, it's not as though anything
really happens around here, is it?

561
01:07:24,424 --> 01:07:28,559
