found something out there.

562
01:07:34,701 --> 01:07:36,167
And I thought to myself...

563
01:07:38,104 --> 01:07:41,605
"What is Jeremy's body
doing buried in my backyard?"

564
01:07:48,248 --> 01:07:50,214
Look...

565
01:07:51,451 --> 01:07:53,320
I'm sure there is some...

566
01:07:53,420 --> 01:07:57,121
