for all of this.

567
01:07:58,492 --> 01:08:00,958
And if there is...

568
01:08:03,230 --> 01:08:06,464
you should tell me
before I call the police.

569
01:08:12,272 --> 01:08:14,084
(PAUL SIGHS)

570
01:08:16,409 --> 01:08:18,443
I'm gonna make the call.

571
01:08:19,579 --> 01:08:21,848
You should stay here.

572
01:08:21,948 --> 01:08:24,482
It can get pretty dangerous outside.

573
01:08:27,587 --> 01:08:30,091
There's nowhere for you to go anyway.

574
01:08:35,762 --> 01:08:37,581
(WIND BLOWING)

575
01:08:49,542 --> 01:08:51,276
(BARKS)

576
01:08:59,152 --> 01:09:00,689
- Come on.
- (BARKING)

577
01:09:16,569 --> 01:09:18,436
(SHADOW BARKING)

578
01:09:38,124 --> 01:09:39,991
(SHADOW WHIMPERING)

579
01:10:03,316 --> 01:10:05,382
