- (POLICE SIRENS WAILING)
- (GLASS BREAKING)

682
01:18:36,762 --> 01:18:38,363
- (GLASS BREAKING)
- Stand down!

683
01:18:39,298 --> 01:18:41,966
Officer, thank God you finally arrived.

684
01:18:43,402 --> 01:18:44,971
