685
01:18:45,071 --> 01:18:46,873
You need to drop that rock, sir.

686
01:18:46,973 --> 01:18:49,142
- No, I know this looks a little weird.
- Drop that rock.

687
01:18:49,342 --> 01:18:52,676
Officer! Please, you have to help me!
Don't listen to him!

688
01:18:53,486 --> 01:18:56,048
I need you to drop the rock, sir.
Right now!

689
01:18:56,148 --> 01:18:58,217
- There's just been a bit of a mis...
- Drop the rock!

690
01:18:58,317 --> 01:19:01,272
Turn and face the window! Turn and face
the window! Hands behind your head.

691
01:19:03,990 --> 01:19:05,412
(BARKING, GROWLING)

692
01:19:06,625 --> 01:19:08,859
Tell your dog to back off!

